UPDATE trans_words SET content_loc4='The mighty creature\'s maw opened wide, tossing bolts of icy water toward our vessel. Those terrible jaws clamped down upon the bow of our ship, tearing it from the hull. Sailors and cargo were thrown violently into the sea as the remnants of the ship disappeared beneath the waves.$B$BThe last thing I remember was flying from the broken hull, hitting the inky waters, and plunging beneath the waves. The world went dark and I thought for certain I\'d drawn my last breath. When I awoke in Theramore\'s infirmary, I knew someone had to tell our story.' WHERE word_id = 125951;
